    "en": {
      "title": "Pilot strike leaves Lufthansa passengers stranded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Pilots at German airline Lufthansa have canceled hundreds of flights across Europe after they launched strike action on Friday.",
        "Lufthansa estimates that more than 130,000 passengers will be affected by the 24-hour strike.",
        "Lufthansa canceled more than 800 of its 1,200 flights scheduled for Friday, hitting the airline hubs of Frankfurt and Munich.",
        "\"A pilot union strike in the middle of the main return travel period at the end of the school holidays in Germany and other European countries will have a massive impact on flight operations,\" Lufthansa said in a statement."
      ],
